    • isProductValid

      public static String isProductValid(String name, int min, int max, int inv, double price, javafx.collections.ObservableList<Part> parts, String errorMessage)
      Validates the product based on various rules.
      Parameters:
      name - Name of the product.
      min - Minimum inventory level for the product.
      max - Maximum inventory level for the product.
      inv - Current inventory level for the product.
      price - Price of the product.
      parts - ObservableList of parts associated with the product.
      errorMessage - The initial error message, usually empty.
      Returns:
      An error message string. If empty, the product is valid.
